  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 947c76105d7454747a8fc8874cd8bff8, type: 3}
  m_Name: EveningNarration 1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::NarrationLines
  lines:
  - Night has fallen over the city.
  - The lights of the buildings flicker in the distance like stars
  - "I\u2019ve had enough time to think of my next move. I can\u2019t let her go
    this time."
  - "Now it\u2019s either I allow her to move on..."
  - Or she dies.
  - I walk up to the old bridge once again.
  - I don't know exactly what outcome to expect here.
  - Anything could happen.
  - I just need to stay calm.
  line: Or she dies.
